iPhone 04:F7:E4:16:75:A3

State: iterate all bulbs and their state, set back the previous state when setting on/off
Timed: fade on to full at 7am.  off at 7:30, on at 3:30, dim at 10, off at 11
Network: On when iPhone is detected, off when gone
Notification: Pulse on event (Growl, Mail, etc).  Color based on value (stock, weather, site activity, network usage)


